  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Bookish</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Connecting book lovers with the perfect reads since 2023</p>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Introduction -->
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Bookish is an online marketplace dedicated to making book discovery and purchasing seamless. 
        We connect book enthusiasts with sellers across the country, offering both new and pre-loved books 
        at competitive prices. Our platform empowers readers to find their next favorite read while 
        helping sellers reach a wider audience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        Whether you're looking for bestsellers, rare finds, or academic texts, Bookish provides 
        a user-friendly platform to browse, purchase, and even sell your books. We believe in 
        building a community where the love for reading is shared and celebrated.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
