          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              To democratize access to knowledge by creating India's most accessible and affordable book marketplace. 
              We aim to connect readers with the books they need, while providing a sustainable platform for booksellers 
              of all sizes to thrive.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start">
