          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Our Vision</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We envision a world where books are accessible to all, where reading is celebrated, and 
              where the joy of discovering new ideas through books is shared by everyone. Bookish aims 
              to be at the forefront of this literary revolution.
            </p>
